# Documentation Sync

## Agent read order

1. `docs/core/01-vision-north-star.md` — product trade-offs
2. `.cursor/rules/project-context.mdc` — code map (this repo's fast index)
3. `docs/core/00-system-index.md` — full docs hub

## When to update docs

| Change | Update |
|--------|--------|
| New feature domain | `docs/features/features-index.md`; optional `feat-*.md` |
| New parser/engine | `docs/logic/logic-index.md` |
| Schema bump | `docs/database/database-index.md` |
| Architectural commit | `project-context.mdc` changelog (see `sync-context-on-commit.mdc`) |
| Large feature | `docs/superpowers/specs/` before coding |
| Strategy pivot | `docs/core/01-vision-north-star.md` + `18-knowledge-capture.md` |
| Session wrap-up | `docs/logs/agent-changelog.md` |

Do **not** hand-edit `public/js/app.bundle.mjs` or chunks. Do **not** auto-modify `docs/superpowers/plans/` unless executing that plan.

Blueprint: `docs/core/17-docs-blueprint.md`
